Recommends: python3-gi, gstreamer1.0-tools, gstreamer1.0-plugins-base, gstreamer1.0-plugins-good, gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad, gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0
Description: VISCA Camera Tracker with YOLOv8 Detection
 Automated camera tracking system for RK3588 with:
  - YOLOv8 object detection (vehicles/faces) via RKNN NPU
  - VISCA camera control (PTZ, exposure, white balance)
  - REST API and MQTT interface
  - Adaptive tracking with persistent gain
  - Hardware-accelerated H.264 streaming
